  <brief_title>Phase 2 Study of Nimotuzumab in Pediatric Recurrent Diffuse Intrinsic Pontine Glioma</brief_title>
  <official_title>Phase 2 Study of Safety and Efficacy of Nimotuzumab (TheraCIMÂ®) in Pediatric Patients With Recurrent Diffuse Intrinsic Pontine Glioma</official_title>
