    <description>150 mg/m2 I.V. Induction phase: infusions once a week for 8 weeks. Consolidation phase: infusions once every 2 weeks for 10 weeks. Patients may then continue on the consolidation regimen of nimotuzumab, until disease progression or the occurrence of unacceptable toxicity.</description>
